        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>&emsp;&emsp;把博客迁移到了Volantis上，很多标签插件用法发生了变化。于是修改这篇文章，以便自己翻阅。</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="文字"><a href="#文字" class="headerlink" title="文字"></a>文字</h2><h3 id="·-首行缩进"><a href="#·-首行缩进" class="headerlink" title="· 首行缩进"></a>· 首行缩进</h3><div class="tabs" id="tab-0"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-0-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-0-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-0-1"><p>&emsp;&emsp;开头要空两个字</p></div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-0-2"><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">&amp;emsp;</span><span class="symbol">&amp;emsp;</span> //每个<span class="symbol">&amp;emsp;</span>空一个汉字</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></div></div><h3 id="·-字体"><a href="#·-字体" class="headerlink" title="· 字体"></a>· 字体</h3><div class="tabs" id="tab-1"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-1-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-1-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-1-1"><p class='p red'>可以改字体的颜色</p><p class='p large'>还可以改字体的大小</p><p class='p logo huge center'>还可以居中使用</p><p class='p logo huge center'>超大毛泽东字体</p>重要的是可以在各级标题中使用</div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-1-2"><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% p [参数1],[参数2],[参数3],[参数4],文字内容 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th><strong>参数类型</strong></th><th><strong>可选值</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>字体</td><td>logo, code</td></tr><tr><td>颜色</td><td>red, yellow, green, cyan, blue, gray</td></tr><tr><td>大小</td><td>small, h4, h3, h2, h1, large, huge, ultra</td></tr><tr><td>对齐方向</td><td>left, center, right</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><h3 id="·-文字样式"><a href="#·-文字样式" class="headerlink" title="· 文字样式"></a>· 文字样式</h3><div class="tabs" id="tab-2"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-2-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-2-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-2-1"><p><u>下划线</u>  <emp>加重号</emp>  <wavy>波浪线</wavy><br><kbd>alt</kbd> + <kbd>f4</kbd>  <psw>黑暗</psw>剑</p></div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-2-2"><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% u 下划线 %&#125;  &#123;% emp 加重号 %&#125;  &#123;% wavy 波浪线 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% kbd 按键图标 %&#125;  &#123;% psw 数据删除 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></div></div><h3 id="·-代码块"><a href="#·-代码块" class="headerlink" title="· 代码块"></a>· 代码块</h3><div class="tabs" id="tab-3"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-3-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-3-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-3-1"><figure class="highlight cs"><figcaption><span>classA</span><a href="https://www.marxists.org/chinese/index.html">还可以留个链接但是不知道有啥用</a></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="built_in">string</span> type = <span class="string">&quot;Code-Block&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    print(type);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-3-2"><ul><li>code：<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// ```[语言类型] [标题] [url] [url标题]</span><br><span class="line">// 代码块</span><br><span class="line">// ```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>需要去掉//注释。一般标题可以用来表示节选的片段属于哪个类/文件。</li></ul></div></div></div><h3 id="·-便条"><a href="#·-便条" class="headerlink" title="· 便条"></a>· 便条</h3><h4 id="1-固定颜色"><a href="#1-固定颜色" class="headerlink" title="1 固定颜色"></a>1 固定颜色</h4><div class="tabs" id="tab-3"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-3-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-3-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-3-1"><div class="note "><p>什么参数都不填的默认效果</p></div><div class="note quote"><p>在你们身上，寄托者人类和中国的将来。&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;————鲁迅</p></div><div class="note info"><p>中性信息</p></div><div class="note warning"><p>警告信息</p></div><div class="note error"><p>错误信息</p></div><div class="note success"><p>正确信息</p></div></div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-3-2"><figure class="highlight mkd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note [参数], 文字内容 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th><strong>效果</strong></th><th><strong>参数</strong></th><th><strong>效果</strong></th><th><strong>参数</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>默认</td><td>留空</td><td>警告信息</td><td>warning</td></tr><tr><td>引用</td><td>quote</td><td>错误信息</td><td>error</td></tr><tr><td>中性信息</td><td>info</td><td>正确信息</td><td>success</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><h4 id="2-可选颜色"><a href="#2-可选颜色" class="headerlink" title="2 可选颜色"></a>2 可选颜色</h4><div class="tabs" id="tab-4"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-4-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-4-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-4-1"><div class="note green"><p>默认+颜色</p></div><div class="note radiation"><p>核能图标</p></div><div class="note radiation yellow"><p>图标+颜色</p></div><div class="note bug red"><p>故障提示</p></div><div class="note link blue"><p>链接</p></div><div class="note paperclip green"><p>附件链接</p></div><div class="note download"><p>下载链接</p></div><div class="note todo clear"><p>代办事项+透明</p></div><div class="note guide"><p>向导</p></div><div class="note message gray"><p>消息</p></div><div class="note up"><p>升级</p></div><div class="note undo light"><p>撤销</p></div><div class="note idea green"><p>想法</p></div></div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-4-2"><figure class="highlight mkd"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note [图标] [颜色], 文字内容 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th><strong>图标</strong></th><th><strong>参数</strong></th><th><strong>颜色</strong></th><th><strong>参数</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>核能</td><td>radiation</td><td>主题色</td><td>留空</td></tr><tr><td>故障</td><td>bug</td><td>淡色</td><td>light</td></tr><tr><td>链接</td><td>link</td><td>灰色</td><td>gray</td></tr><tr><td>附件</td><td>paperclip</td><td>红色</td><td>red</td></tr><tr><td>下载</td><td>download</td><td>黄色</td><td>yellow</td></tr><tr><td>代办事项</td><td>todo</td><td>绿色</td><td>green</td></tr><tr><td>向导</td><td>guide</td><td>青色</td><td>cyan</td></tr><tr><td>消息</td><td>message</td><td>蓝色</td><td>blue</td></tr><tr><td>升级</td><td>up</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>撤销</td><td>undo</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>想法</td><td>idea</td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><h3 id="·-增强版便条"><a href="#·-增强版便条" class="headerlink" title="· 增强版便条"></a>· 增强版便条</h3><div class="tabs" id="tab-4-1"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-4-1-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-4-1-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-4-1-1"><div class="note todo"><p><strong>待办事项</strong></p><p>可以写换行的，<br>增强版便条。</p><div class="note success"><p>可以嵌套普通便条</p></div>其他东西也可以嵌套。<div class="note warning"><p>但是由于会分不清endnoteblock的原因，不能直接嵌套增强版便条。</p></div></div></div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-4-1-2"><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;fa FontAwesome图标名&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>直接去<a href="https://fontawesome.com/" title="FontAwesome">FontAwesome</a>复制就行。</p></div></div></div><h3 id="·-图标"><a href="#·-图标" class="headerlink" title="· 图标"></a>· 图标</h3><div class="tabs" id="tab-5"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-5-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-5-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-5-1"><p><i class="fab fa-steam"></i> <i class="fas fa-robot"></i></p></div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-5-2"><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;fa FontAwesome图标名&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div></div></div><p>直接去<a href="https://fontawesome.com/" title="FontAwesome">FontAwesome</a>复制就行。</p><h3 id="·-Emoji"><a href="#·-Emoji" class="headerlink" title="· Emoji"></a>· Emoji</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;🌶️💩💉💧🐂🍺<br>&emsp;&emsp;直接去<a href="https://emojipedia.org/" title="EmojiPedia">EmojiPedia</a>复制。</p><h3 id="·-选框"><a href="#·-选框" class="headerlink" title="· 选框"></a>· 选框</h3><p>&emsp;&emsp;用来丰富文本的选框图示，并没实际的选框功能</p><h4 id="1-单选项"><a href="#1-单选项" class="headerlink" title="1 单选项"></a>1 单选项</h4><div class="tabs" id="tab-6"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-6-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-6-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-6-1"><div class='checkbox'><input type="radio" />            <p>未选中</p>            </div><div class='checkbox checked'><input type="radio" checked="checked"/>            <p>选中</p>            </div><div class='checkbox blue'><input type="radio" />            <p>未选中+蓝色</p>            </div><div class='checkbox checked blue'><input type="radio" checked="checked"/>            <p>选中+蓝色</p>            </div></div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-6-2"><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% radio [checked] [颜色], 文本内容 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>checked留空表示未选中。</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>颜色</strong></th><th><strong>参数</strong></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>红色</td><td>red</td></tr><tr><td>黄色</td><td>yellow</td></tr><tr><td>绿色</td><td>green</td></tr><tr><td>青色</td><td>cyan</td></tr><tr><td>蓝色</td><td>blue</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><h4 id="2-复选项"><a href="#2-复选项" class="headerlink" title="2 复选项"></a>2 复选项</h4><div class="tabs" id="tab-7"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-7-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-7-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-7-1"><div class='checkbox'><input type="checkbox" />            <p>未选中</p>            </div><div class='checkbox checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>选中</p>            </div><div class='checkbox blue'><input type="checkbox" />            <p>未选中+蓝色</p>            </div><div class='checkbox checked blue'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>选中+蓝色</p>            </div></div><div class="tab-pane" id="tab-7-2"><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% checkbox [checked] [颜色], 文本内容 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参数和单选框相同</p></div></div></div><h2 id="图表"><a href="#图表" class="headerlink" title="图表"></a>图表</h2><h3 id="·-图片"><a href="#·-图片" class="headerlink" title="· 图片"></a>· 图片</h3><h4 id="1-单张图片"><a href="#1-单张图片" class="headerlink" title="1 单张图片"></a>1 单张图片</h4><div class="tabs" id="tab-tubiao"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><a class="#tab-tubiao-1">效果</a></li><li class="tab"><a class="#tab-tubiao-2">写法</a></li></ul><div class="tab-content"><div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-tubiao-1"><div class="img-wrap"><div class="img-bg"><img class="img lazyload" src="https://gitee.com/giresharu/img-depository/raw/master/image.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://gitee.com/giresharu/img-depository/raw/master/image.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="小秦和爽爽子"/></div><span class="image-caption">小秦和爽爽子</span></div><div class="img-wrap"><div class="img-bg"><img class="img lazyload" src="https://gitee.com/giresharu/img-depository/raw/master/image.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://gitee.com/giresharu/img-depository/raw/master/image.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="宽度400像素的小秦和爽爽子" style="width:400px;"/></div><span cl